statement: imarnf1pr $p |- ( ( X e. V /\ Y e. W ) -> ( ( ( F : { X , Y } --> dom E /\ E : dom E --> R ) /\ ( ( E ` ( F ` X ) ) = A /\ ( E ` ( F ` Y ) ) = B ) ) -> ( E " ran F ) = { A , B } ) ) $.
